data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! MOTIVATED SELLER! This beautiful Windemere Original Home! Great Location! Move in ready with a pool and screened in lanai! House is on a double lot, almost 1/2 Acre of land! Great with 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with open floor plan. All you need is in this house, spacious family area, great lanai with pool to enjoy with your family! Beautiful Fantasy Brown Granite Island in the kitchen and gorgeous cabinets. Master bedroom also has slider to the pool area plus a master suite complete with a soaking tub and a separate shower. Interior freshly painted, NO CDD, NO HOA, Not in a flood zone.  Located near restaurants and shopping. You also have several beaches about 30 minutes away. Don't miss this opportunity!
